}

query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## List User Business Unit
  แสดงรายการหน่วยธุรกิจของผู้ใช้ทั้งหมดพร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและค้นหา

  Lists all user-to-property access assignments across the platform, showing which users have been granted access to which hotel properties. Used for multi-tenant access management and auditing.

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `page` | number | No | 1 | Page number |
  | `perpage` | number | No | 10 | Items per page |
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  Platform admin only — managed at Keycloak realm role level

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
        "user_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "business_unit_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "role": "user",
        "is_default": true,
        "is_active": true,
        "audit": {
          "created": { "at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z", "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890", "name": "John Doe" },
          "updated": { "at": "2026-04-29T09:15:00.000Z", "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567891", "name": "Jane Smith" }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
        "user_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4e",
        "business_unit_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4f",
        "role": "user",
        "is_default": false,
        "is_active": true,
        "audit": {
          "created": { "at": "2026-04-29T08:00:00.000Z", "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890", "name": "John Doe" }
        }
      }
    ],
